Olive Oil
1 bag Asian Stir-Fry Mix
1 packet beef strips
1 packet garlic paste
1 packet flat noodles
1 sachet oyster sauce
1 sachet sweet chilli sauce
1 packet Crispy Shallots
1 bunch coriander

Heat olive oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat.
Cook stir-fry mix until softened, 3 mins.
Transfer to a bowl and set aside.
Return pan to high heat. Cook beef and garlic paste, tossing, until browned, 1-2 mins.

Meanwhile, poke a few holes in noodle packet and microwave until steaming, 2 mins.

Now, add oyster sauce, sweet chilli sauce, noodles and veggie mix to the beef.
Season to taste and toss to combine.
Divide noodle stir-fry between plates.
Top with crispy shallots and torn coriander.